Hello,

We are having the first introductory session in
*CRC from 5:30 - 8:00 today(17/09/2016).*
It will be an introduction session to the amazing world of robotics.
There will be some on-spot registrations too. So if any of your friends
have missed the deadline, then they can still be a part of the workshop

The only pre-requisite is loads of ENTHU!.

So reserve your seats and enjoy the enthralling world of robotics


